reviewText: The volume is too low- Hard to hear her speaking over background noises
Fun video...ready to go to England!
I find Ian Wright and Justine Shapiro very entertaining in travel videos.
Just love Ian with Globe Trekker! Good condition, quick ship, good price, thank you.

Just bought this trekker dvd and  after watching the series for over 10yrs vote this as one of the best. I have come to enjoy Justine and Ian as hosts and bring a lot of excitement to travel [the way it should be!] This dvd and megan mcCormick's Scotland are in my opinion, the best in the series!

One can never learn enough nor explore enough of London and Britain.

My girl friend enjoyed this show tremendously and learned a couple of new ways to explore the land.
I teach British and American literature and show these episodes to my students as a previewer to the course.  They love them.  I love them.  Highly recommended to teachers.
